  "texts": [
    "Weight limits can also be used to capture the portfolio manager's views on how the market will evolve.",
    "For example, she might insist on a long position for some assets, and a short position for some others.",
    "When a benchmark is used, we can impose limits on active weights.",
    "For example |ww b | ≤ 0.10 means that no asset in the portfolio can be more than 10% over-weight or under-weight.",
    "Leverage limit."
  ],
